column1:
Mmhm, no mistake there. I'm not picking up
any enemy readings.
We scraped by... That was unbelievably rough.
That should've taken care of the Jails, too.

Top-notch work, you guys. That was some
legitimate hero action back there.

Why're you talking like you weren't in there?
You're a hero too, Wolf.

I'm a... hero. A knight in shining armor. That
doesn't sound bad at all, right, Joker?

A knight in shining armor, huh? Never
expected my little joke to actually come
true.

Looks like it's starting—the fusion of reality
and the Metaverse is coming undone.
Now's the time to make our escape!
Oh yeah, we need to bring Ichinose with us!

I will go get her. You should all head back
now.
All right, let's get out of here!
